  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/f29a07b9c20caf66ed7a88e27bb93767.poster.avif?t=1750430761\" width=616 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/f29a07b9c20caf66ed7a88e27bb93767.webm?t=1750430761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/1bc4b95b9b4def34e2c87f5d14aab5db.avif?t=1750430761\" width=600 height=295 /></span><br><br><strong>Hostlight is a challenging single-player first-person puzzle game that will embark you on a mysterious adventure. Solve puzzles by using LIGHTS AND SHADOWS, and discover what lies ahead in an intriguing tower.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/e1f88a1471930e7484e36d011e574fd9.poster.avif?t=1750430761\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/e1f88a1471930e7484e36d011e574fd9.webm?t=1750430761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/e1f88a1471930e7484e36d011e574fd9.mp4?t=1750430761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/e847da44754e3020f6dd6a42391d5be0.avif?t=1750430761\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br><br>o\t<strong>Use your brain to complete intriguing and challenging puzzles</strong> by using lights and shadows with innovative gameplay mechanics.<br><br>o\t<strong>Create the pieces</strong> required to solve the puzzles through the use of projected shadows. <br><br>o\t<strong>Lights and shadows</strong> can be projected by manipulating silhouettes that hit the player to obtain the necessary pieces.<br><br>o\tPlay around with the <strong>primary light colours</strong> (Red, Green, and Blue) to mix and match and complete puzzles. Only the white light creates objects!<br><br>o\t<strong>Take advantage of the environment</strong> — Use mirrors to direct light beams and use rails.<br><br>o\tTo <strong>complete from one level to another</strong> you need to light up the platform in the middle of each room.<br><br>o\t<strong>Play through over 20 levels</strong>, each designed to offer different puzzles and challenges. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/fa1afdebd0b73997c70fd2356686a2ac.poster.avif?t=1750430761\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/fa1afdebd0b73997c70fd2356686a2ac.webm?t=1750430761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/fa1afdebd0b73997c70fd2356686a2ac.mp4?t=1750430761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/1bc4b95b9b4def34e2c87f5d14aab5db.avif?t=1750430761\" width=600 height=295 /></span><br><br><strong>Hostlight is a challenging single-player first-person puzzle game that will embark you on a mysterious adventure. Solve puzzles by using LIGHTS AND SHADOWS, and discover what lies ahead in an intriguing tower.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/e1f88a1471930e7484e36d011e574fd9.poster.avif?t=1750430761\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/e1f88a1471930e7484e36d011e574fd9.webm?t=1750430761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/e1f88a1471930e7484e36d011e574fd9.mp4?t=1750430761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/e847da44754e3020f6dd6a42391d5be0.avif?t=1750430761\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br><br>o\t<strong>Use your brain to complete intriguing and challenging puzzles</strong> by using lights and shadows with innovative gameplay mechanics.<br><br>o\t<strong>Create the pieces</strong> required to solve the puzzles through the use of projected shadows. <br><br>o\t<strong>Lights and shadows</strong> can be projected by manipulating silhouettes that hit the player to obtain the necessary pieces.<br><br>o\tPlay around with the <strong>primary light colours</strong> (Red, Green, and Blue) to mix and match and complete puzzles. Only the white light creates objects!<br><br>o\t<strong>Take advantage of the environment</strong> — Use mirrors to direct light beams and use rails.<br><br>o\tTo <strong>complete from one level to another</strong> you need to light up the platform in the middle of each room.<br><br>o\t<strong>Play through over 20 levels</strong>, each designed to offer different puzzles and challenges. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/fa1afdebd0b73997c70fd2356686a2ac.poster.avif?t=1750430761\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/fa1afdebd0b73997c70fd2356686a2ac.webm?t=1750430761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824110/extras/fa1afdebd0b73997c70fd2356686a2ac.mp4?t=1750430761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
